text: The following lists events that happened during 2013 in Cuba. ==Incumbents== *President: Raúl Castro *Vice President: José Ramón Machado Ventura (until 24 February), Miguel Díaz-Canel (starting 24 February) *Prime Minister: Raúl Castro *President of the National Assembly: Ricardo Alarcón (until 24 February), Esteban Lazo Hernández (starting 24 February) ==Events== ==References==
title: 2013 in Cuba
